2.54_SCREWTERM for use with  PRT-10571.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

3.5mm Screw Terminal footprints for  PRT-08084&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

5mm Screw Terminal footprints for use with PRT-08432</description>
